asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: Born in Durban, a small wealthy country on the coast of South Africa, BlackJack moved to Miami, in the US, shortly after he sold his family discovered the largest discovery of diamonds in history. He now lives the life of a modern day Rico Suave, loves to play cards and never loses, even when he loses the hand. BlackJack lives a carefree, luxury lifestyle and has a confidence in the tone of his voice that is commanding, yet kind. The ladies love this furry black beach bunny. The fellas envy him.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

description: Al Bunny Borland was a famous character in the 90s TV show Burrow Improvement.  He was famously known for wearing his multitudes of flannel shirts, and more importantly, for stopping his cohost Tim from doing stupid things on the set of Tool Time.  After the show stopped airing, Bunny Borland eventually retired to heaven and was given angel status for the way he put up with all of Tims antics.  He did not get there unscarred though.  His ear was injured from a stupid antic that Tim did one time with a power tool, and it serves as memory as to why he got his halo.

description: Ok, fluffle, first theres something you should know. Its not pronounced vibes anymore. Its pronounced wybes. W Y B E S. And please, move your head on your shoulders as you say it. My sister, Ivory, is also super talented. Her DJ name is Double Sleeve. Our names clearly reflect our parents obsession with musical instruments and thats what we are here for. You. Music. Wybes. Love. The feels. Fluf World. You want me to bring the wybe up, or to slow it down, Im your gal. Just wait until we are partying in the meta verse. Its going to be sik.
